reasoning_2:
∑_{n=1}^∞ (1/3)^n is a geometric series with first term a = 1/3 and ratio r = 1/3.  
Sum = a/(1 - r) = (1/3)/(1 - 1/3) = (1/3)/(2/3) = 1/2.  
\boxed{\frac{1}{2}}

